title: Lennon Stella Performs 'Telescope' With Hayden Panettiere on 'Nashville' - Watch Here!
text: Lennon Stella Performs 'Telescope' With Hayden Panettiere on 'Nashville' - Watch Here! Monday, 26 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) Maddie (Lennon Stella) gets a hug from Juliette (Hayden Panettiere) in this clip from the most recent episode of Nashville. In the episode, Juliette shared the spotlight with Maddie during her concert in Atlanta, and performed “Telescope” with her!
